OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777907466
OL,3,CWreck of torpedoed American ship
OL,4,Cdiscovered off Cornwall 108 years later
OL,6,FAn American ship which sank after it
OL,7,Fwas torpedoed by a German submarine
OL,8,Fduring World War I has been discovered
OL,9,Foff the coast of Newquay.
OL,11,FThe U.S. Coast Guard Cutter Tampa was
OL,12,Fhit in the Bristol Channel by a German
OL,13,FU-boat in September 1918.
OL,15,FShe sank in just three minutes with
OL,16,Fall 131 people - including American
OL,17,Fand British naval personnel and
OL,18,Fcivilians - on board.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
