FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777907466
OL,3,CWreck of torpedoed American ship
OL,4,Cdiscovered off Cornwall 108 years later
OL,6,FIt was the largest single American
OL,7,Fnaval combat loss of life in the First
OL,8,FWorld War.
OL,10,FThe wreck was discovered 50 miles from
OL,11,Fthe coast, and more than 300 feet
OL,12,Fdeep, by the Gasperados Dive Team.
OL,14,F"This discovery is the result of three
OL,15,Fyears of research and exploration,"
OL,16,Fsaid Team Leader Steve Mortimer.
OL,18,F"Tampa is of huge importance to the
OL,19,FUnited States and the relatives of
OL,20,Feveryone who died that day.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777907466
OL,3,CWreck of torpedoed American ship
OL,4,Cdiscovered off Cornwall 108 years later
OL,6,F"Their final resting place is known at
OL,7,Flast."
OL,9,FThe team of volunteer divers worked
OL,10,Fwith historians and the U.S. Coast
OL,11,FGuard in their search for the wreck.
OL,13,F"When the Tampa was lost with all
OL,14,Fhands in 1918, it left an enduring
OL,15,Fgrief in our service," said Adm. Kevin
OL,16,FLunday, commandant of the U.S. Coast
OL,17,FGuard.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
