OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777907466
OL,3,CWreck of torpedoed American ship
OL,4,Cdiscovered off Cornwall 108 years later
OL,6,F"Locating the wreck connects us to
OL,7,Ftheir sacrifice and reminds us that
OL,8,Fdevotion to duty endures. We will
OL,9,Falways remember them."
OL,11,FThe Gasperados Team say they are now
OL,12,Fworking with the Coastguard on next
OL,13,Fsteps for the discovered wreck.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
